{"type": "article", "id": 4732, "title": "巴黎世家大理石运动鞋", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-26T08:00:34Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233534CjT9upRYDH45fL7E.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t现在的运动鞋款已不只满足于在运动领域有所作为了，拼了命地往时尚圈挤。各种撞色、涂鸦、材质拼接元素齐上阵，还不时跟明星推出联名款。不过，这款巴黎世家（Balenciaga）最新发布的大理石运动鞋还是给人眼前一亮的感觉，设计师对大理石花纹的运用，简直相似到肉眼会误以为把大理石穿在脚上，搭配巴黎世家运动鞋的经典廓形与厚橡胶鞋底，潮味十足。定价 3777 元，<a href=\"http://www.mrporter.com/en-cn/mens/balenciaga/suede-trimmed-marbled-leather-and-rubber-sneakers/509571\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233531lFJmHgMOiZzTGB7n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233532DdzkrVGLb2oNwmOY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052335321Tw4WzE9lGspRLJD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233532TCXkycWKqm0EM6tu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233533JqljP0SpV3ns41C5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.04375\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;line-height:normal;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}